1 Praise Jah
I will praise Jehovah with all my heartב In the assembled group of upright ones and in the congregation
 2 The works of Jehovah are great They are studied by all those finding pleasure in them
 3 His activity is glorious and splendid And his righteousness endures forever
 4 He causes his wonderful works to be remembered
Jehovah is compassionate and merciful
 5 Food he gives to those fearing him
He remembers his covenant forever
 6 He has revealed to his people his powerful worksל By giving them the inheritance of the nations
 7 The works of his hands are truth and justice Trustworthy are all his orders
 8 They are always reliable now and forever They are made in truth and righteousness
 9 He has given redemption to his people
He commanded that his covenant should last forever
His name is holy and awe-inspiring
10 The fear of Jehovah is the beginning of wisdom
All those observing his orders show good insight
His praise endures forever
